snippet.title: Overwatch Street Date Reveal
snippet.description:
Your watch is about to begin! Overwatch launches May 24:  http://www.buyoverwatch.com  

Want a head start on all the heroic action? Join us May 5-9 for the Overwatch Open Beta. Pre-purchase digitally or preorder at participating retailers and unlock early access* to the Open Beta for you and a friend starting May 3! For more details, visit: http://blizz.ly/1U5gi77 

*Early Access offer ends April 29, 2016. 

Like Us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/playoverwatch   
Follow Us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/playoverwatch
